                        <persName xml:lang="fa" type="alt">مرزا محمد حسن بن محمد علي</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_9529">Mirʼāt-i Aḥmadī</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_9529">مرآت احمدي</title>
                     <note>Folio one, recto: title in read, probably by original rubricator, and presentation stamp, as on Nos 82 and 83. The Khatimah or conclusion, giving an extensive account of the City and Subah of Ahmadabad. Uniform with Nos. 82 and 83, containing the earlier portions of the work. Scribe: Shiv La'l son of Sundar La'l Nakir Ahmadabadi. Written for John Romer. Rubrication as on No 82.</note>
                     <incipit>Khatimah dar bayan-i bana wa 'ard wa tul wa daur-i hisar-i shahr-panah</incipit>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl>As for RAS Persian MSS Nos 82 and 83.</bibl>
                     </listBibl>
